1. Ti *uzimaš* knjigu sa police. (You take the book from the shelf.)
2. On *uzima* novac iz novčanika. (He takes money from his wallet.)
3. Kada *uzmeš* kafu, donesi mi i jednu. (When you take coffee, bring me one too.)
4. Mi *uzimamo* uzorke zemljišta radi analize. (We take soil samples for analysis.)
5. Vi *uzimate* prednosti u ovoj situaciji. (You take advantage in this situation.)
6. Oni *uzimaju* previše vremena na sastanku. (They take too much time in the meeting.)
7. Da li ćeš *uzimati* učešće u projektu? (Will you take part in the project?)
8. Uzmi ovaj ključ i *uzmi* mi auto u servis. (Take this key and take my car to the service.)
9. *Uzimajući* u obzir sve činjenice, ovo je najbolje rešenje. (Taking into account all the facts, this is the best solution.)
10. Ne *uzimaj* previše stvari sa sobom na putovanje. (Don't take too many things with you on the trip.)